      "back": "أنا سعيد.",
      "romanized": "ana sa'id.",
      "grammarNote": "Arabic drops 'to be' in the present. أنا (I) + سعيد (happy, masc.) = 'I am happy.' Female speaker: أنا سعيدة (ana sa'ida)."
